content.en_US: [[Fraction|Fractioning Tower]] of [[cracked naphtha|Cracked Naphtha]]. Similarly to diesel, it is [[cracked|Catalytic Cracking Tower]] or [[mixed|Industrial Mixer]] with [[reformate|Reformate]] to obtain cracked high-cetane diesel. Cracked Diesel and cracked high-cetane diesel are hydrotreated to obtain [[diesel|Diesel]] and [[high-cetane diesel|High-Cetane Diesel]].
